OL,7,FThe leader of Leicester City Council
OL,8,Fhas warned bankruptcy is a "real
OL,9,Fprospect" for the authority without
OL,10,Ffurther government support.
OL,12,FMayor Sir Peter Soulsby said the
OL,13,Fcouncil was "running out of options"
OL,14,Fto balance its books in a letter to
OL,15,Fthe Levelling Up Secretary, Michael
OL,16,FGove.
OL,18,FHe also claimed the government did
OL,19,Fnot have "the slightest awareness" of
OL,20,Fthe impact of rising costs.
